-- ThyssenKrupp to Name Gabriele Sons Head of Personnel, FTD Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-04-18T19:19:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-18/thyssenkrupp-to-name-gabriele-sons-head-of-personnel-ftd-says.html
ThyssenKrupp AG (TKA)  will probably name
Gabriele Sons to its executive board as head of personnel,
replacing Ralph Labonte,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported,
without citing anyone.  Sons would be the first woman on the company’s board, the
newspaper said, adding that the decision hasn’t been finalized.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  